WEBVTT

01:34.560 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:40.040 --> 01:41.480
I heard that someone
saw them holding hands

01:41.560 --> 01:43.520
on the first day of school.

01:44.040 --> 01:44.920
Really?

01:45.000 --> 01:46.080
- For real?
- Yes.

01:46.160 --> 01:47.440
- Are you serious?
- No wonder

01:47.520 --> 01:49.200
they've been late
these past couple of days.

01:49.280 --> 01:51.280
Rumor has it they were already
a thing in middle school.

01:52.560 --> 01:53.520
Middle school?

01:54.040 --> 01:55.680
- That's interesting.
- Yeah.

01:55.760 --> 01:57.120
But isn't that too early
for middle schoolers?

01:57.200 --> 01:58.920
Guess that's just
the way it is these days.

02:00.760 --> 02:02.960
Girls, let's hurry up.

02:03.040 --> 02:04.560
The boys will be coming in to change soon.

02:17.920 --> 02:19.920
Did you hear what they said?

02:23.320 --> 02:25.240
Are you just going to let them gossip?

02:25.920 --> 02:26.960
What else can I do?

02:28.120 --> 02:30.600
Do you think those guys
have a crush on you?

02:34.600 --> 02:37.240
Are you not changing
into your sports uniform?

02:38.600 --> 02:39.600
I am.

03:22.960 --> 03:25.120
Why are you secretly following me?

03:26.120 --> 03:27.880
I'm following you openly.

03:31.600 --> 03:32.560
Wen Yifan,

03:33.120 --> 03:37.400
do you know
there's a profession called a pacer?

03:38.600 --> 03:39.600
I don't.

03:40.120 --> 03:42.040
A pacer is someone who runs
with others to help them train.

03:46.680 --> 03:47.680
I can't go on.

03:49.640 --> 03:52.400
So, are you my pacer?

03:57.800 --> 04:00.680
You're the one pacing me.

04:02.240 --> 04:03.480
Can't run anymore?

04:06.360 --> 04:07.280
Your shoelace came undone.

04:08.560 --> 04:10.040
Your shoelace came undone.

04:27.200 --> 04:28.440
3,063 DAYS

04:28.520 --> 04:34.080
DAY 1 OF OFFICIAL COHABITATION

04:34.160 --> 04:35.040
Helping with the move, sir?

04:35.120 --> 04:37.040
- Yes, 1701.
- Don't move.

04:37.120 --> 04:38.960
Sorry about that. You go first.

04:44.840 --> 04:46.120
What's going on?

04:51.120 --> 04:52.120
Sorry.

04:58.560 --> 04:59.960
What's going on here?

05:00.680 --> 05:03.040
Nothing. Just adding some furniture.

05:05.160 --> 05:06.320
That's quite a lot.

05:20.360 --> 05:22.080
Enjoying the sunshine?

05:34.040 --> 05:36.080
Sorry, this isn't mine.

05:36.160 --> 05:37.520
Your boyfriend told me to put this here.

05:42.920 --> 05:44.600
Did they deliver this
to the wrong address?

05:45.760 --> 05:47.400
It was a bundle deal with a discount.

05:47.480 --> 05:48.320
The cat tree was a free add-on.

05:48.400 --> 05:50.360
If you don't need it,
feel free to get rid of it.

06:43.040 --> 06:46.360
Dian, Sang Yan got this for you.

06:55.880 --> 06:57.000
That's a lot.

06:57.080 --> 06:58.280
18,000
ACCEPT TRANSFER

07:04.560 --> 07:05.600
ACCEPT TRANSFER

07:05.680 --> 07:06.800
NOW LOADING

07:17.360 --> 07:20.200
520
ACCEPT TRANSFER

07:36.600 --> 07:37.600
What's this supposed to mean?

07:38.120 --> 07:39.640
Here, play with this.

07:46.240 --> 07:47.440
What's this supposed to mean?

07:49.840 --> 07:51.320
This is the money I'm returning to you.

07:56.200 --> 07:57.720
Why is it such an awkward amount?

08:10.800 --> 08:12.880
EXPENSE BREAKDOWN

08:12.960 --> 08:14.720
4,000 FOR DEPOSIT, 12,000 FOR RENT
200 FOR ELECTRICITY

08:18.640 --> 08:21.160
Don't misunderstand.
This is the expense breakdown.

08:21.240 --> 08:23.720
You sent more than necessary,
so I returned the extra.

08:28.480 --> 08:31.800
Do you want to double-check?

08:37.840 --> 08:39.520
18,000 MINUS 4,000 FOR DEPOSIT
12,000 FOR RENT

08:39.600 --> 08:41.520
200 FOR ELECTRICITY
90 FOR WATER, 105 FOR INTERNET

08:41.600 --> 08:44.520
200 FOR PROPERTY MANAGEMENT
AND 900 FOR PARKING

08:52.920 --> 08:54.960
Would he think I did it on purpose?

08:55.760 --> 08:58.160
It's okay. I understand.
It's just a miscalculation.

08:58.240 --> 08:59.920
This is beyond embarrassing.

09:04.000 --> 09:06.200
Thanks for reminding me. Sorry, I…

09:06.280 --> 09:07.840
It should have been 505.

09:07.920 --> 09:10.360
I sent ten, no, 40…

09:10.920 --> 09:12.400
I mean, 15 more by mistake.

09:12.480 --> 09:14.280
You can just refund me on WeChat.

09:15.960 --> 09:17.800
Why did I send him 520
and make it look like a love confession?

09:21.120 --> 09:22.520
I'd rather be a fool and send 250 instead.

09:56.280 --> 09:57.800
Hello?

09:57.880 --> 09:58.920
Qiao.

09:59.000 --> 10:01.720
Mom, why are you calling
when we're both at home?

10:01.800 --> 10:02.920
Is breakfast ready?

10:03.000 --> 10:04.120
You're thinking about breakfast?

10:04.200 --> 10:06.440
You were out all night

10:06.520 --> 10:08.000
and now you want…?

10:08.080 --> 10:08.960
I…

10:09.840 --> 10:11.440
was out the whole night?

10:20.080 --> 10:21.840
Mom, I'll hang up now. I'll be home soon.

10:32.720 --> 10:34.320
Why was the curtain suddenly opened?

10:34.400 --> 10:35.600
How did I end up here?

10:38.040 --> 10:38.880
Who are you?

10:41.360 --> 10:42.840
- Why are you here?
- How should I know?

10:45.840 --> 10:47.400
What's wrong with you?

11:00.720 --> 11:03.200
Sang Yan, I guess
you're not completely heartless.

11:11.360 --> 11:13.240
I already gave you the pickup code.

11:13.760 --> 11:14.920
I don't want the bag anymore.

11:15.000 --> 11:16.160
You can leave now.

11:18.360 --> 11:20.440
We used to go to the same school,

11:20.520 --> 11:22.200
so I thought I'd check in on you.
Are you okay?

11:25.960 --> 11:28.040
Does drinking like that even taste good?

11:28.720 --> 11:30.040
Don't worry.

11:30.120 --> 11:31.040
That's just how he is after a breakup.

11:31.880 --> 11:34.240
We are all used to watching him
chase after lost causes.

11:34.320 --> 11:35.160
Pass me the drink.

11:38.200 --> 11:39.160
Here's your whiskey.

11:39.880 --> 11:40.960
Go easy on it.

11:41.040 --> 11:42.280
Stop nagging. I can hold my liquor.

11:42.920 --> 11:44.320
Then I'll drink with you.

11:46.320 --> 11:47.760
- What do you want?
- Where are my clothes?

11:47.840 --> 11:50.280
How would I know where your clothes are?
Where are my clothes?

11:50.360 --> 11:51.720
This is your place. Why are you asking me?

12:02.320 --> 12:03.880
Did we…?

12:03.960 --> 12:05.040
We didn't.

12:09.120 --> 12:10.640
It's all a blur.

12:11.160 --> 12:13.440
I can't remember.
We probably didn't if I don't remember.

12:14.040 --> 12:15.400
We definitely didn't. I'm sure of it.

12:15.480 --> 12:16.600
Yes. That's good.

12:16.680 --> 12:17.840
What's that supposed to mean?

12:17.920 --> 12:19.520
What? I could be the one
being taken advantage of.

12:19.600 --> 12:20.840
Where's my top?

12:20.920 --> 12:22.160
Did you hide it?

12:22.240 --> 12:23.200
What about my clothes then?

12:23.280 --> 12:25.120
Stop running around my house!

12:28.800 --> 12:30.960
Your place is such a mess.

12:31.040 --> 12:32.600
That's why I told you not to run around.

12:35.000 --> 12:36.480
How did I even get in here?

12:39.520 --> 12:40.480
THE MAIN ENTRANCE TO THE UPPER DISTRICT

12:40.560 --> 12:42.000
See? Please explain

12:42.080 --> 12:44.360
why you're following me.

12:44.440 --> 12:45.640
The driver made me get out of the car.

12:45.720 --> 12:47.640
Wasn't it you who brought me
back to your place?

12:48.160 --> 12:50.120
You were throwing up so badly.
I just helped you up.

12:50.200 --> 12:51.280
I didn't want you to come with me.

12:51.360 --> 12:52.840
You could have just let me sleep there.

12:52.920 --> 12:54.120
Why did you help me?

12:54.200 --> 12:55.400
Do you think I'm that kind of person?

12:55.480 --> 12:56.440
Of course, I had to help you up,

12:56.520 --> 12:58.880
but I didn't expect you to cling to me.

13:01.800 --> 13:03.320
OUTSIDE THE ELEVATOR

13:03.400 --> 13:04.920
Why did you carry me on your back?

13:05.000 --> 13:07.160
I never said I would carry you.
You got on my back by yourself.

13:07.240 --> 13:08.320
Show me the proof.

13:08.400 --> 13:09.600
- Why are you blaming me?
- Keep playing.

13:09.680 --> 13:10.640
Keep playing.

13:10.720 --> 13:12.040
INSIDE THE ELEVATOR

13:12.120 --> 13:14.120
You even asked me to dance.
Look at yourself.

13:15.560 --> 13:19.000
Honestly, from what I saw on the footage,

13:19.080 --> 13:20.280
it looked like a mutual thing.

13:21.160 --> 13:23.800
So, why is it no longer mutual now?

13:23.880 --> 13:25.320
None of your business.

13:26.440 --> 13:27.560
Just keep watching.

13:28.080 --> 13:30.960
OUTSIDE THE ELEVATOR ON THE THIRD FLOOR

13:31.040 --> 13:32.400
Bye.

13:35.040 --> 13:36.840
Our cameras can only monitor up to here.

13:36.920 --> 13:39.160
What happened after you closed the door

13:39.240 --> 13:40.120
is out of our hands.

13:40.760 --> 13:42.200
We didn't do anything.

15:18.200 --> 15:19.240
Help yourself.

15:27.080 --> 15:28.280
Dig in. Why aren't you eating?

15:28.360 --> 15:30.320
You… Is it not to your taste?

15:31.440 --> 15:33.400
No. I'll eat it.

15:44.920 --> 15:46.880
We've cleared up the misunderstanding.

15:48.080 --> 15:49.400
Come on. Let's have a toast.

16:00.120 --> 16:03.320
XIANG LANG: QIAO, I'VE LANDED
WHERE ARE YOU?

16:04.320 --> 16:06.280
All right, I'll be there soon.

16:06.360 --> 16:07.240
I'm done eating. I'm off.

16:12.960 --> 16:14.160
On the right.

16:19.840 --> 16:21.080
How do you open this door?

16:35.040 --> 16:36.360
It's probably because
of the dry weather lately.

16:43.840 --> 16:45.040
Thanks.

17:13.119 --> 17:14.720
He drinks such high-quality coffee.

17:25.079 --> 17:25.960
Hello, Qiao.

17:26.040 --> 17:28.280
Dian, I've found you a roommate.

17:28.359 --> 17:29.640
A roommate?

17:30.880 --> 17:32.600
- Dian.
- Xiang Lang?

17:32.680 --> 17:35.680
Didn't I ask you to hide?
Now there's no surprise.

17:36.200 --> 17:37.680
It's still a surprise.

17:37.760 --> 17:40.080
Qiao, how come you didn't even tell me?

17:40.160 --> 17:41.520
I told you before, okay?

17:41.600 --> 17:43.600
I've told you several times
that he's coming back.

17:43.680 --> 17:45.400
You just didn't listen to me properly.

17:45.480 --> 17:47.200
I might have accidentally forgotten.

17:47.920 --> 17:49.640
- Where are you guys now?
- At the airport.

17:49.720 --> 17:52.640
I originally thought of asking you
to come pick him up with me,

17:52.720 --> 17:55.480
but they said they were worried
about you being busy with work

17:55.560 --> 17:57.080
and didn't want you to get up so early.

17:57.680 --> 17:59.720
- Morning.
- Morning.

17:59.800 --> 18:01.760
I did just wake up.

18:02.360 --> 18:03.920
Xiang Lang also needs to rent
a place now that he's back.

18:04.000 --> 18:05.240
Maybe you two could be roommates?

18:09.520 --> 18:12.200
I forgot to tell you,
but I found a roommate.

18:12.280 --> 18:13.160
Who is it?

18:17.040 --> 18:19.960
Should we pick a day to hang out together?

18:20.040 --> 18:21.040
We definitely should.

18:21.120 --> 18:22.640
It's been years.

18:22.720 --> 18:24.400
How about Thursday?
I'm not working that day.

18:24.480 --> 18:25.800
Just don't bail on us.

18:25.880 --> 18:27.640
Don't worry. I won't.

18:27.720 --> 18:29.000
Thursday it is then.

18:29.080 --> 18:30.920
- Bye.
- Bye.

18:31.520 --> 18:32.600
Love you.

18:41.000 --> 18:42.120
Are you going out?

18:43.920 --> 18:44.920
My old friend, Xiang Lang,

18:46.840 --> 18:48.280
is back in the country.

18:49.040 --> 18:50.680
We were in Class 17 in high school,

18:50.760 --> 18:52.720
and he and Qiao were in Class 15.

18:53.480 --> 18:56.400
The three of us
grew up together in kindergarten.

18:57.280 --> 18:58.200
You must know him, right?

19:01.160 --> 19:02.400
It doesn't ring a bell.

19:12.600 --> 19:14.640
Have you picked a spot for the gathering?

19:14.720 --> 19:15.880
Not yet.

19:18.480 --> 19:20.160
How about Overtime?

19:21.320 --> 19:23.680
Since we're roommates,
you can help bring in more customers.

19:25.120 --> 19:26.640
Has your business gotten so bad

19:27.160 --> 19:29.120
that you need to personally
bring in customers?

19:30.800 --> 19:32.920
I've told you before
that it's not making much money.

19:33.000 --> 19:35.600
We have to find ways to promote it
and get more customers.

19:39.960 --> 19:41.200
What do you think?

19:45.360 --> 19:46.440
I can give you a roommate discount.

19:48.320 --> 19:49.600
What's the discount?

19:51.480 --> 19:53.000
Let's say…

19:56.200 --> 19:57.240
One percent.

19:58.200 --> 19:59.680
- Come again?
- One percent.

20:04.680 --> 20:05.560
How generous.

20:06.480 --> 20:08.200
- I'll consider it.
- It's decided then.

20:08.280 --> 20:09.720
Thursday.

20:09.800 --> 20:11.480
I've saved you a spot for Thursday.

20:20.080 --> 20:21.720
Honestly, the first time
I went to your gastropub,

20:21.800 --> 20:22.640
I spent ages looking for it.

20:22.720 --> 20:25.080
It took me forever
to find the Overtime sign.

20:25.920 --> 20:27.320
I didn't exactly want to walk in,

20:29.000 --> 20:30.440
looking at it from the outside.

20:34.080 --> 20:35.240
What do you mean?

20:36.640 --> 20:38.480
I just mean the sign isn't obvious,

20:39.160 --> 20:40.680
and it doesn't really
look like a place to eat.

20:40.760 --> 20:42.120
It looks more like a barbershop.

20:42.640 --> 20:44.880
But, of course,
that's just my personal opinion.

20:44.960 --> 20:46.360
No need to take it to heart.

20:50.360 --> 20:52.960
Since it was so unnoticeable and so bad,

20:54.280 --> 20:55.880
why did you come in the first place?

21:01.120 --> 21:02.440
Headliner.

21:03.280 --> 21:04.680
It's because you…

21:06.240 --> 21:07.360
I got it.

21:07.440 --> 21:10.320
I'll think about your comment,
but I won't change it.

21:15.720 --> 21:16.720
Thursday, okay?

21:21.920 --> 21:24.080
So, here's the story.

21:24.160 --> 21:26.680
Since she's my roommate,
I didn't feel right saying no,

21:26.760 --> 21:29.600
so I ended up buying these
low-quality products from her.

21:29.680 --> 21:31.080
She's clearly taking advantage of me.

21:31.160 --> 21:32.920
I'm going to sue her, and I won't stop

21:33.000 --> 21:34.680
- until she loses everything.
- A 1% discount.

21:35.200 --> 21:36.760
Isn't that taking advantage of me, too?

21:36.840 --> 21:39.480
She swindled all my savings away.

21:39.560 --> 21:41.000
I worked for two years to earn that money.

21:41.080 --> 21:42.280
What's the rush?

21:42.360 --> 21:44.440
She took all of it, a total of 50,000.

21:49.520 --> 21:51.320
You seem a bit down recently.

21:51.400 --> 21:52.480
Here's a coffee for you.

21:53.720 --> 21:54.760
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

21:55.520 --> 21:56.680
No worries.

21:58.040 --> 22:00.000
Eat this to regain some energy.

22:00.760 --> 22:02.640
Isn't eating not allowed
in the cutting room?

22:02.720 --> 22:04.920
I call the shots in this room. Eat.

22:06.240 --> 22:07.160
Thanks.

22:08.880 --> 22:11.040
This software has a shortcut key.
Here, let me show you.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.920
What are you doing?

22:24.640 --> 22:25.800
I'm sorry, I…

22:25.880 --> 22:27.240
Sorry, I'll go find someone
to clean this up.

22:29.240 --> 22:30.240
Is that necessary?

22:30.320 --> 22:31.880
Everyone knows what you are like.

22:35.000 --> 22:36.120
Let's go.

22:45.600 --> 22:47.840
Wen, you've seen
the newspaper today, right?

22:47.920 --> 22:49.240
Your article wasn't included.

22:49.760 --> 22:51.160
Sorry, sir.

22:51.240 --> 22:53.040
I'll keep trying my best.

22:54.760 --> 22:56.080
It's actually quite simple.

22:58.200 --> 23:00.760
YIHE DAILY

23:00.840 --> 23:03.000
Do you know

23:03.960 --> 23:05.240
where the problem lies?

23:06.640 --> 23:07.800
I know,

23:09.240 --> 23:10.080
but I can't do it.

23:13.360 --> 23:16.200
Also, please don't text me
in the middle of the night anymore.

23:16.720 --> 23:19.640
Yifan, why are you here alone?

23:19.720 --> 23:20.880
Are you okay?

23:28.600 --> 23:29.760
Or have you heard about it?

23:30.960 --> 23:32.120
Heard about what?

23:33.040 --> 23:35.200
Lately, everyone's
been gossiping about you.

23:35.280 --> 23:38.600
They say when you were at Yihe Daily,
the boss's wife came after you,

23:38.680 --> 23:40.840
and then the local press blacklisted you.

23:41.360 --> 23:44.120
You couldn't handle it anymore,
so you secretly returned to Nanwu.

23:47.040 --> 23:49.200
Those who spread rumors
really overestimate me,

23:49.280 --> 23:50.320
saying I was blacklisted.

23:51.640 --> 23:54.480
Pretty girls always get
caught up in rumors like this.

23:54.560 --> 23:56.160
I've told them
that it's definitely not true.

23:56.240 --> 23:58.840
You should go explain it to them quickly.

23:58.920 --> 24:00.640
Do you think they'll
believe me even if I explain?

24:01.280 --> 24:03.240
You vixen, wait and see
how I deal with you today.

24:03.320 --> 24:04.640
Get out of the way!

24:05.360 --> 24:06.480
You're Wen Yifan, aren't you?

24:08.200 --> 24:09.040
You vixen.

24:09.120 --> 24:10.000
You're the one
who sent late-night messages

24:10.080 --> 24:10.920
to flirt with my husband, right?

24:11.000 --> 24:11.840
Shameless!

24:12.680 --> 24:14.680
You shameless wretch!

24:15.280 --> 24:16.840
What are you doing with your phone?
Let me tell you.

24:16.920 --> 24:18.880
- I won't believe a word you say today!
- Take a good look.

24:19.640 --> 24:21.480
It's your husband
who's been sending me messages,

24:21.560 --> 24:22.920
and I've never replied
with anything inappropriate.

24:23.000 --> 24:24.440
I don't want to hear your nonsense.

24:24.520 --> 24:25.720
You'll see how I deal with you today.

24:25.800 --> 24:27.000
It takes two to tango.

24:27.080 --> 24:28.280
Keep this up,
and you'll make the headlines.

24:29.120 --> 24:31.040
It's clearly the wrongdoer's fault,

24:31.120 --> 24:33.160
yet the victim bears the blame.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.440
Do you really believe

24:35.040 --> 24:37.320
those words were said unconsciously
because he was drunk?

24:37.400 --> 24:39.160
I'll write an investigation report
and send it

24:39.760 --> 24:40.920
to the president

24:41.000 --> 24:43.080
and the newly formed
supervisory committee.

24:43.160 --> 24:46.080
However, I'm not sure
what the result will be.

24:46.760 --> 24:48.920
- Why?
- He must have his side of the story.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.400
After all, this isn't the first time.

24:56.520 --> 24:57.640
But if you don't say anything,

24:57.720 --> 25:00.080
they'll assume you're admitting it.

25:00.160 --> 25:01.400
Whether I admit it or not,

25:01.480 --> 25:04.160
they'll only believe
what they want to believe.

25:05.400 --> 25:07.480
Rumors are like wounds.

25:08.200 --> 25:09.480
If you don't pay attention to them,

25:11.120 --> 25:12.440
they'll stop hurting after a while.

25:15.840 --> 25:17.080
Don't worry about me. I'm fine.

25:18.400 --> 25:19.600
What time is it now?

25:20.680 --> 25:21.880
It's almost three o'clock.

25:22.640 --> 25:23.720
I'll go out for an interview now.

25:27.760 --> 25:29.880
All right, Mr. Chen, let's get started.

25:29.960 --> 25:32.920
Could you walk us through
what happened during the incident?

25:33.520 --> 25:35.800
That night, my daughter was helping me out

25:36.480 --> 25:37.640
at the snack stall after school.

25:38.240 --> 25:40.160
Three men at a table were drunk.

25:40.840 --> 25:42.480
My daughter's only 16,

25:42.560 --> 25:44.520
but they kept harassing her.

25:45.120 --> 25:46.760
At that moment, all I could think

25:46.840 --> 25:48.480
was if they laid a finger on her, I'd…

25:49.520 --> 25:50.760
- Dad.
- Are you okay?

25:50.840 --> 25:51.880
- Careful.
- I'm fine.

25:51.960 --> 25:52.920
Are you all right, Dad?

25:53.000 --> 25:55.120
It's all my fault.

25:55.200 --> 25:57.280
You are hurt because of me.

25:57.360 --> 25:58.360
This injury's nothing.

25:58.440 --> 25:59.560
I'd be heartbroken

25:59.640 --> 26:01.280
if I hadn't kept you safe.

26:02.000 --> 26:05.120
It's because of me. It's all my fault.

26:05.200 --> 26:06.240
It's not your fault.

26:08.040 --> 26:09.120
Yifan,

26:10.400 --> 26:12.360
this child is only 16.

26:13.280 --> 26:15.240
Yet their family had to go through
such an ordeal.

26:17.080 --> 26:19.480
It's like misfortune always targets
the most vulnerable.

26:22.040 --> 26:24.240
But I filmed everything
that happened just now.

26:24.320 --> 26:26.280
That kid was crying,
and it was heartbreaking.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.080
Wen Yifan?

26:35.560 --> 26:36.560
It really is you.

26:37.360 --> 26:38.200
How come you're back in Nanwu?

26:39.040 --> 26:40.480
I moved back to Nanwu.

26:40.560 --> 26:42.240
- Yifan, maybe I should…
- No need.

26:42.320 --> 26:44.000
We're busy right now.
Let's get in touch later.

26:44.080 --> 26:46.920
Who do you think you are?
Who wants to get in touch with you?

26:47.000 --> 26:48.840
Yifan, how about I go back
to the car first and sort things out?

26:48.920 --> 26:49.880
You guys can chat.

26:51.400 --> 26:52.520
Thank you.

26:57.880 --> 26:59.400
Why are you back if there's nothing wrong?

27:00.040 --> 27:01.480
Why can't I come back
even if nothing's wrong?

27:02.440 --> 27:03.800
I didn't mean it that way.

27:04.320 --> 27:05.280
Don't worry.

27:05.360 --> 27:07.600
I won't be staying at your place
now that I'm back in Nanwu.

27:07.680 --> 27:09.000
Let's just pretend we never met today.

27:09.080 --> 27:10.840
As long as you don't say anything,
no one will know.

27:11.360 --> 27:13.480
I never said
you couldn't come to my place.

27:17.360 --> 27:18.520
You didn't.

27:20.960 --> 27:23.120
Why are you being so annoying?

27:24.720 --> 27:26.800
Fine. I was at fault back then.

27:26.880 --> 27:27.960
I was young and didn't know better.

27:28.040 --> 27:29.840
I was wrong to ask you to leave my house.

27:29.920 --> 27:30.920
All right.

27:33.000 --> 27:36.400
I don't want to bring up the past,
nor do I think we need to catch up.

27:37.920 --> 27:39.280
That stuff is heavy, right?

27:39.360 --> 27:40.640
Go check on the patient.

27:42.200 --> 27:43.680
Will you go back home
for the Spring Festival?

27:43.760 --> 27:45.040
I have to work during the Spring Festival.

27:45.560 --> 27:46.800
All right, let's add each other on WeChat.

27:46.880 --> 27:49.240
No need. I just want to live my own life.

27:50.080 --> 27:50.920
You…

27:53.640 --> 27:55.520
My return to Nanwu
has nothing to do with anyone.

27:55.600 --> 27:58.320
I won't stay at your place,
and it's not because I'm afraid of you.

28:01.440 --> 28:03.720
Every decision I make is for myself.

28:03.800 --> 28:05.040
I'm actually busy. I'll get going now.

28:11.040 --> 28:13.760
Dad, look. It's snowing outside.

28:14.880 --> 28:17.280
It really is snowing. Pretty, isn't it?

28:17.360 --> 28:18.440
Yes.

28:18.520 --> 28:20.160
- Isn't it lovely?
- It is.

28:20.240 --> 28:21.480
- Are you happy?
- Yes.

28:21.560 --> 28:24.120
Let's have a snowball fight later.

28:28.920 --> 28:31.680
- It's snowing.
- It's snowing.

28:32.400 --> 28:33.480
Let me lift you up.

28:38.000 --> 28:40.560
Jiang, do you know
how you got your nickname?

28:41.160 --> 28:42.480
I don't.

28:43.440 --> 28:46.640
It's because you were born

28:46.720 --> 28:49.080
on the day of Frost's Descent.

28:51.240 --> 28:52.600
What exactly is Frost's Descent?

28:53.200 --> 28:54.800
Frost's Descent happens

28:55.320 --> 28:57.320
in late September of the lunar calendar,

28:57.400 --> 28:59.040
when the sun

28:59.120 --> 29:01.920
is farther away from Earth.

29:02.600 --> 29:05.760
It's the day
with the largest temperature difference

29:05.840 --> 29:07.560
between day and night,

29:08.080 --> 29:11.680
making the night particularly cold.

29:12.280 --> 29:15.000
But I'm afraid of the cold.

29:15.600 --> 29:18.400
Don't be afraid, Jiang, I'm here.

29:35.760 --> 29:37.800
When you're cold, just come to me.

29:38.320 --> 29:41.320
I'll hold you tight,
and you won't feel cold anymore.

30:30.080 --> 30:31.000
Wen Yifan,

30:33.960 --> 30:37.240
I have a little flaw about me.

30:38.640 --> 30:39.800
Only one?

30:41.800 --> 30:44.360
I'm very safety-conscious.

30:44.880 --> 30:46.800
If I don't lock the door
before going to bed,

30:46.880 --> 30:47.960
I can't sleep.

30:48.960 --> 30:50.520
I always lock the door.

30:51.040 --> 30:52.240
If you're tired, go ahead and sleep.

30:52.320 --> 30:53.880
I'll lock it if I get back late.

30:53.960 --> 30:56.160
I'm talking about before sleeping.

30:58.880 --> 31:00.480
I remember telling you explicitly

31:01.000 --> 31:02.880
before we started sharing the apartment

31:02.960 --> 31:04.040
that I frequently work overtime

31:04.120 --> 31:05.720
and have an irregular routine.
You agreed to it.

31:05.800 --> 31:08.760
Then, please let me know in advance

31:12.120 --> 31:13.320
if you're coming back after 10 p.m.

31:14.400 --> 31:16.680
- Why?
- It's a matter of mutual respect.

31:18.520 --> 31:19.800
If you don't come back all night,

31:19.880 --> 31:22.160
wouldn't I have to spend
the night in anxiety and fear?

31:28.080 --> 31:29.680
I'll let you know next time.

31:30.840 --> 31:31.760
Can I go rest now?

31:40.280 --> 31:41.680
Who is he?

31:42.280 --> 31:43.560
I forgot to tell you. He's my friend.

31:45.720 --> 31:47.560
Hi, I am Duan Jiaxu.

31:52.880 --> 31:54.440
I heard from Su Haoan

31:54.520 --> 31:57.400
that Sang Yan didn't date a single girl
during his four years at university.

31:57.480 --> 31:59.720
He spent all his time
hanging out with a campus heartthrob

31:59.800 --> 32:01.040
named Duan Jiaxu.

32:05.720 --> 32:08.280
Duan Jiaxu, I've heard a lot about you.

32:09.640 --> 32:11.360
I also have a flaw.

32:12.160 --> 32:14.480
My safety awareness
is stronger than someone else's,

32:14.560 --> 32:16.440
and I remember we have a contract clause.

32:16.520 --> 32:17.800
I don't quite recall.

32:18.800 --> 32:20.480
You should inform me in advance
before bringing friends home.

32:20.560 --> 32:22.040
All right. I remember now.

32:23.240 --> 32:24.080
I'm sorry.

32:25.160 --> 32:26.040
It's okay.

32:26.800 --> 32:29.240
We're still getting used
to living together,

32:29.320 --> 32:31.560
so small mistakes are excusable.

32:35.400 --> 32:37.600
I'll let it slide this time.
You two catch up.

32:43.720 --> 32:45.440
I told you to leave earlier,
but you didn't listen.

32:45.960 --> 32:47.800
You even spilled food on your clothes.

32:57.760 --> 32:59.720
So, where do you think
we should go on Thursday?

32:59.800 --> 33:00.680
How about Overtime?

33:00.760 --> 33:01.640
Sang Yan opened it.

33:01.720 --> 33:03.160
Sang Yan?

33:03.960 --> 33:05.160
You are still in touch?

33:05.240 --> 33:08.240
I only met him recently,
and it was at his gastropub.

33:08.320 --> 33:10.720
So, uh, I need to tell you something.

33:10.800 --> 33:13.520
Remember I told you I have a roommate?

33:14.240 --> 33:15.560
Well, that roommate

33:16.280 --> 33:17.400
is Sang Yan.

33:17.480 --> 33:19.640
He said if we go to his place,
he'll give us a discount.

33:20.240 --> 33:22.800
You're actually sharing
a place with Sang Yan?

33:22.880 --> 33:24.560
And what discount do we get?

33:24.640 --> 33:25.840
Let's talk about it when we meet.

33:25.920 --> 33:27.000
I still have to get
some work done tonight.

33:27.080 --> 33:27.920
I'm going to log off now.

33:28.000 --> 33:30.520
Wait. How much
of a discount are we getting?

33:31.080 --> 33:33.480
One percent.

33:33.560 --> 33:35.040
One percent?

33:35.120 --> 33:36.680
I'll log off now. Bye.

33:38.440 --> 33:39.800
Wait. Did I hear that right?

33:39.880 --> 33:41.600
Is a 1% discount
still considered a discount?

33:43.880 --> 33:45.560
Let's go with Dian's choice this time.

33:45.640 --> 33:47.280
We've always picked the places before.

33:47.360 --> 33:48.800
It's rare for her to have an opinion.

33:48.880 --> 33:50.360
You're totally on her side, huh?

33:50.440 --> 33:52.880
Wait until we meet,
I'll crack open her brain

33:52.960 --> 33:54.880
and see what's going on in there.

33:54.960 --> 33:56.720
Why would she share a place with Sang Yan?

33:56.800 --> 33:57.920
I really don't get it.

33:59.320 --> 34:00.680
It's getting late, Qiao.

34:00.760 --> 34:01.800
You should go to bed now.

34:03.240 --> 34:05.480
- All right, then. Goodnight.
- Night.

34:31.239 --> 34:33.159
- Hello.
- Dian, are you ready?

34:33.239 --> 34:34.880
- We're here.
- You are already here?

34:34.960 --> 34:37.040
So soon? Just give me a moment.

34:37.120 --> 34:39.199
The car isn't allowed to enter,
so I've just parked it at the entrance.

34:39.280 --> 34:41.199
All right, I just finished
washing the clothes.

34:41.280 --> 34:42.679
I'll be out as soon as I hang them up.

34:42.760 --> 34:44.320
It's okay. No rush. Take your time.

34:45.320 --> 34:47.679
Who says there's no rush?
I'm about to die of hunger.

34:47.760 --> 34:48.760
Dian, hurry up.

34:51.440 --> 34:52.840
I'll save your life in a minute.
Got to go now.

34:55.880 --> 34:56.960
Hey,

34:57.800 --> 34:59.240
did you save a spot for us at Overtime?

34:59.960 --> 35:03.200
We're going to eat first.
We'll be at Overtime around eight.

35:54.280 --> 35:55.400
Are you heading out too?

36:00.920 --> 36:02.640
When did you change your clothes?

36:14.920 --> 36:16.120
Are you going to the garage?

36:24.080 --> 36:26.360
Well… We haven't reached
the basement level yet.

36:26.440 --> 36:27.640
This is the first floor.

36:36.360 --> 36:40.680
UPTOWN FLOWER CITY

36:40.760 --> 36:41.880
Let's go.

36:42.800 --> 36:43.640
Dian.

36:47.920 --> 36:49.480
Dian. It's been a while.

36:49.560 --> 36:52.320
- It's been a while.
- Why are you two acting shy?

36:52.400 --> 36:54.120
The Nanwu Trio is finally united.

36:54.200 --> 36:55.840
From now on, we'll overcome
all obstacles and be invincible.

36:56.560 --> 36:57.600
Who is this?

37:06.480 --> 37:07.360
Is this your boyfriend?

37:09.480 --> 37:10.680
What boyfriend?

37:10.760 --> 37:12.080
This is Xiang Lang.

37:12.640 --> 37:14.680
Xiang Lang. I remember.

37:16.520 --> 37:17.600
- You are from Class 15.
- Yes.

37:17.680 --> 37:18.520
- I'm Su Haoan.
- Hi.

37:20.480 --> 37:21.520
Sang Yan.

37:23.240 --> 37:24.120
Long time no see.

37:33.120 --> 37:34.280
Didn't we agree that you'd drive your car?

37:35.640 --> 37:36.760
I can't be bothered to drive.

37:37.800 --> 37:38.640
I drove here.

37:38.720 --> 37:39.840
Where do you need to go?

37:40.520 --> 37:41.400
It's fine.

37:41.480 --> 37:43.160
We'll just find somewhere to eat.

37:43.240 --> 37:45.120
Didn't you guys already make plans?
You can go ahead.

37:46.640 --> 37:48.400
We really haven't met in a long time.
We should definitely catch up.

37:49.360 --> 37:50.640
It's been a while
since we last met as well.

37:52.760 --> 37:54.640
Why make such a big deal of it?
You're not really close with them.

37:54.720 --> 37:56.360
Even if we're not close,
we can still catch up,

37:59.000 --> 38:00.760
- right?
- Yeah.

38:00.840 --> 38:01.960
So, you want to go with them, right?

38:02.800 --> 38:05.200
- Is it all right?
- I don't think so.

38:05.280 --> 38:06.640
I think it's pretty all right.

38:06.720 --> 38:07.960
Where's your car?

38:21.120 --> 38:21.960
Open the door.

38:22.600 --> 38:23.800
Yes, boss.

38:25.040 --> 38:26.880
It's amazing how fate works.

38:26.960 --> 38:28.160
You haven't seen a friend
in seven or eight years,

38:28.240 --> 38:29.080
and then you just run into them like this.

38:29.160 --> 38:31.040
If Sang Yan and Wen Yifan
can be roommates,

38:31.120 --> 38:33.360
what else is impossible?

38:33.440 --> 38:35.200
Since there are so many of us,
I'll tidy up the car first.

38:35.280 --> 38:36.880
I'll help you.

38:39.360 --> 38:41.720
I know this is definitely something
worth bragging about.

38:42.480 --> 38:43.480
What are you talking about?

38:44.200 --> 38:47.520
There's no need to bring up
our shared rental to everyone.

38:51.960 --> 38:53.040
We'll manage
if the five of us squeeze a bit.

38:54.120 --> 38:55.160
This should be all right.

38:56.040 --> 38:57.960
Dian, you sit in the passenger seat
and help me with the navigation.

39:02.200 --> 39:04.400
My legs are too long.
It's uncomfortable sitting in the back.

39:05.080 --> 39:06.320
You can just go straight.

39:10.240 --> 39:11.080
Okay.

39:13.280 --> 39:15.320
It's fine, I'll sit in the back.

39:15.400 --> 39:17.040
- Is that okay?
- Sure. No worries.

39:47.320 --> 39:50.160
- I can't see the road with you like this.
- Well, then pay attention to the road.

39:57.280 --> 39:58.440
Have you got a girlfriend?

40:05.360 --> 40:08.200
No. I still haven't met the person I like.

40:19.000 --> 40:20.400
I just thought of a rumor.

40:22.320 --> 40:23.920
Sang Yan, Xiang Lang, and Wen Yifan,

40:24.000 --> 40:25.600
they said you three
were in a love triangle.

40:25.680 --> 40:26.880
Is it true?

40:30.360 --> 40:31.720
It was all just rumors.

40:32.240 --> 40:34.800
It got passed on and started
to sound like it was real.

40:34.880 --> 40:35.880
It simply wasn't true.

40:35.960 --> 40:37.360
What do you mean
by "sound like it was real?"

40:37.960 --> 40:39.680
You're really into gossip
and just making things up.

40:39.760 --> 40:41.480
What I'm saying is true.

40:42.000 --> 40:43.120
If you don't believe me, ask Sang Yan.

40:43.200 --> 40:45.360
He even got into a fight over it.

40:46.160 --> 40:47.600
I heard from Zhou Zhiming

40:47.680 --> 40:49.920
that Pretty Face Wen
doesn't actually like Sang Yan.

40:50.000 --> 40:53.280
She only got together with him
because he kept pursuing her.

40:53.800 --> 40:56.400
So, when she met someone better,
she immediately cheated.

40:56.480 --> 40:58.440
Who's better?

40:58.520 --> 41:00.040
It's Xiang Lang from the class next door.

41:16.840 --> 41:17.960
If I didn't tell you,

41:18.040 --> 41:19.840
would you think
Pretty Face Wen is this kind of person?

41:19.920 --> 41:21.920
It's really quite disgusting.

41:22.000 --> 41:23.480
- Indeed.
- But why?

41:25.200 --> 41:28.040
She thinks being
good-looking makes her great.

41:28.840 --> 41:30.520
There are a lot
of good-looking people out there.

41:30.600 --> 41:31.520
Surely they won't all act like this.

41:31.600 --> 41:32.520
Let me tell you this.

41:32.600 --> 41:35.360
With an attitude like yours,
what's the point of being pretty?

41:39.400 --> 41:40.920
- Apologize.
- I'm sorry.

41:42.680 --> 41:44.280
I'm not asking you to apologize.

41:44.360 --> 41:47.280
Zhou Zhiming, do I need to teach you?

41:47.360 --> 41:48.400
I won't apologize.

41:50.960 --> 41:51.960
I was just joking earlier,

41:52.040 --> 41:55.680
- and I'm not the only one saying this.
- Joking?

41:55.760 --> 41:58.440
You're a man with such a sharp tongue.
Aren't you embarrassed?

41:59.400 --> 42:00.560
Let me make this clear today.

42:01.160 --> 42:03.120
If anyone dares spread such rumors again,

42:03.880 --> 42:05.440
the consequences will be the same as his.

42:06.240 --> 42:07.800
I don't have many hobbies.

42:08.480 --> 42:09.640
I just like holding grudges.

42:10.560 --> 42:11.520
Talk.

42:11.600 --> 42:14.280
Pretty Face Wen… No, Wen Yifan,

42:14.800 --> 42:16.000
I'm sorry.

42:16.080 --> 42:19.360
It was me who told others
you were cheating,

42:19.440 --> 42:20.400
but I had no proof.

42:20.480 --> 42:23.160
I was just making things up.
I won't say it again in the future.

42:23.240 --> 42:25.480
Is that enough? Can you let me go now?

42:35.640 --> 42:36.520
What about me?

42:37.400 --> 42:38.520
Am I not also a victim?

42:39.520 --> 42:42.560
Sang Yan, I'm sorry.

42:44.520 --> 42:45.360
Why are you a victim?

42:48.360 --> 42:50.840
Can you spread rumors
according to the facts?

42:51.360 --> 42:53.040
What do you mean
the other person found someone better

42:53.120 --> 42:54.400
and dumped me?

42:54.480 --> 42:57.600
If I were actually
pursuing them that hard,

42:58.120 --> 43:01.600
they'd be completely captivated by me.

43:02.800 --> 43:03.920
Understand?

43:06.040 --> 43:07.720
- Yes.
- Louder.

43:08.400 --> 43:09.360
Yes!

43:23.520 --> 43:24.720
Thank you.

43:25.440 --> 43:27.440
He doesn't even know who's better.

43:30.320 --> 43:32.680
Sang Yan has always been
a stickler for details since he was a kid.

43:32.760 --> 43:34.480
He doesn't talk much,
but whenever he does, he's ready to fight.

43:34.560 --> 43:35.840
He has a terrible temper.

43:37.720 --> 43:38.920
I'm all right.

43:39.000 --> 43:41.360
See? He loves hitting others.

43:41.440 --> 43:42.760
Wen Yifan,

43:42.840 --> 43:45.560
I'm sorry I didn't tell you in advance
about Sang Yan moving in.

43:45.640 --> 43:47.480
I heard it shocked you.
I'll pay for the meal later.

43:48.200 --> 43:49.200
No need.

43:49.280 --> 43:50.720
This has nothing to do with you.

43:51.880 --> 43:52.920
Sang Yan,

43:53.800 --> 43:56.320
did you know in advance
that your roommate would be Dian?

43:59.960 --> 44:00.800
Yes,

44:02.720 --> 44:04.600
that's why I decided to move in.

44:27.640 --> 44:29.200
I thought of another rumor.

44:32.720 --> 44:38.400
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

45:00.800 --> 45:02.320
Why is she still here?

45:03.240 --> 45:04.200
Excuse me.

45:08.120 --> 45:09.240
Excuse me.

45:09.800 --> 45:12.040
Our dance class has booked this slot.

45:12.120 --> 45:14.200
I think I still have
ten more minutes left.

45:14.920 --> 45:16.280
She's new here, isn't she?

45:17.280 --> 45:18.520
Who cares whether she is or not?

45:18.600 --> 45:20.360
Her dancing isn't impressive.

45:21.200 --> 45:22.360
I don't know why she's trying so hard.

45:22.960 --> 45:24.520
She's just arrogant.

45:25.520 --> 45:27.720
We booked this dance studio.

45:27.800 --> 45:29.360
Can you leave now?

45:33.760 --> 45:35.800
You're just dancing around by yourself,
taking up all this space.

45:35.880 --> 45:36.720
It's really unnecessary.

45:39.720 --> 45:41.080
Didn't she say
there are still ten minutes left?

45:42.320 --> 45:43.360
Also,

45:45.520 --> 45:46.560
who says she's by herself?

45:48.880 --> 45:50.720
She even found someone to help her.

45:50.800 --> 45:52.400
Does she really think she's so great?

45:52.480 --> 45:54.120
So what if you've brought help?

45:54.640 --> 45:56.080
Can you two just take over
the whole dance studio?

45:56.160 --> 45:58.320
Who is she? I've never seen her before.

49:18.560 --> 49:19.400
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

49:19.480 --> 49:20.840
TREAT YOURSELF WELL, AND THE WORLD
WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
